Symbol.Script_1D:
! const values for parameter: iBarkMaterial PLANTMAT_BARK1 = 1 PLANTMAT_BARK2 = 2 PLANTMAT_BARK3 = 3 PLANTMAT_BARK4 = 4
! const values for parameter: iLeaveMaterial PLANTMAT_LEAFS1 = 1 PLANTMAT_LEAFS2 = 2 PLANTMAT_LEAFS3 = 3 PLANTMAT_LEAFS4 = 4
EPS = 0.00001
! const values for parameter: iDetlevel3D DETLEVEL3D_DETAILED = 1 DETLEVEL3D_SIMPLE = 2 DETLEVEL3D_OFF = 3
PLANT_TYPE1 = 1 PLANT_TYPE2 = 2 PLANT_TYPE3 = 3 PLANT_TYPE4 = 4 PLANT_TYPE5 = 5
dim stDetlevel3D[3] stDetlevel3D[1] = `Детальный` stDetlevel3D[2] = `Простой` stDetlevel3D[3] = `Откл.`
dim stPlantType[5] stPlantType[1] = `Растение 01` stPlantType[2] = `Растение 02` stPlantType[3] = `Растение 03` stPlantType[4] = `Растение 04` stPlantType[5] = `Растение 05`
if iBarkMaterial = PLANTMAT_BARK1 then mat1 = "bark01" if iBarkMaterial = PLANTMAT_BARK2 then mat1 = "bark02" if iBarkMaterial = PLANTMAT_BARK3 then mat1 = "bark03" if iBarkMaterial = PLANTMAT_BARK4 then mat1 = "bark04"
if iLeaveMaterial = PLANTMAT_LEAFS1 then mat2 = "leafs1" if iLeaveMaterial = PLANTMAT_LEAFS2 then mat2 = "leafs2" if iLeaveMaterial = PLANTMAT_LEAFS3 then mat2 = "leafs3" if iLeaveMaterial = PLANTMAT_LEAFS4 then mat2 = "leafs4"
n=nlef ! Leafs Number
dr=0.15
Symbol.Script_VL:
call "FM_types" parameters all
values{2} "iDetlevel3D" DETLEVEL3D_DETAILED, stDetlevel3D[1], DETLEVEL3D_SIMPLE, stDetlevel3D[2], DETLEVEL3D_OFF, stDetlevel3D[3]
values "gs_resol" range [3, ) values "zzyzx" range [0.25, )
values{2} "iBarkMaterial" PLANTMAT_BARK1, `Кора 1`, PLANTMAT_BARK2, `Кора 2`, PLANTMAT_BARK3, `Кора 3`, PLANTMAT_BARK4, `Кора 4`
values{2} "iLeaveMaterial" PLANTMAT_LEAFS1, `Листья 1`, PLANTMAT_LEAFS2, `Листья 2`, PLANTMAT_LEAFS3, `Листья 3`, PLANTMAT_LEAFS4, `Листья 4`
if gs_cont_pen=0 then parameters gs_cont_pen=4 if gs_fill_pen=0 then parameters gs_fill_pen=91
values{2} "iRoomPlantType" PLANT_TYPE1, stPlantType[1], PLANT_TYPE2, stPlantType[2], PLANT_TYPE3, stPlantType[3], PLANT_TYPE4, stPlantType[4], PLANT_TYPE5, stPlantType[5]
if iDetlevel3D = DETLEVEL3D_SIMPLE then lock "gs_resol"
if GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "iRoomPlantType" then if iRoomPlantType = PLANT_TYPE1 then a = 0.4 b = 0.4 zzyzx = 0.8 else if iRoomPlantType = PLANT_TYPE2 then a = 0.64 b = 0.64 zzyzx = 0.45 else if iRoomPlantType = PLANT_TYPE3 then a = 0.381 b = 0.528 zzyzx = 1 else if iRoomPlantType = PLANT_TYPE4 then a = 0.847 b = 0.693 zzyzx = 1.451 else a = 0.549 b = 0.514 zzyzx = 1.36 endif endif endif endif parameters a = a, b = b, zzyzx = zzyzx endif
if iRoomPlantType = PLANT_TYPE3 then if GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "A" then B=A*1.385826 PARAMETERS B=B else A=B*0.72159 PARAMETERS A=A endif else if GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "A" then B=A PARAMETERS B=B else A=B PARAMETERS A=A endif endif
if iRoomPlantType = PLANT_TYPE4 |\ iRoomPlantType = PLANT_TYPE5 then hideparameter "nlef" lock "nlef" endif
hideparameter "gs_onorm_Title"
! ============================================================================= ! UI ! =============================================================================
values "gs_ui_current_page" 1
Symbol.Script_UI:
TABID_ROOT = -1 TABID_TYPE = 1
ui_current_page gs_ui_current_page
!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!! *** Page 1 *** !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!! ui_page TABID_TYPE, TABID_ROOT, `Тип Растения`, "uiTab_Style_flat(1)"
pageStartY = 5
ui_infield{3} "iRoomPlantType", 0, pageStartY, 444, 260, 1, 1, ! ui_PlantTypes.png 5, 2, 105, 123, 100, 100, 1, stPlantType[1], PLANT_TYPE1, 2, stPlantType[2], PLANT_TYPE2, 3, stPlantType[3], PLANT_TYPE3, 4, stPlantType[4], PLANT_TYPE4, 5, stPlantType[5], PLANT_TYPE5
